{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/css/css-basic/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jane's PS Blog","author":"[Jisun Lim]","siteUrl":"https://janeljs.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"janeljs/janeljs.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"janeljs"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"93916a44-50cd-5628-94da-c6c2215f065d","excerpt":"CSS Cascading Style Sheets HTML 문서를 시각적으로 예쁘게 꾸며준다. Cascading(위에서부터 우선순위) Author style User style Browser !important cascading을 끊어내고 가장 우선순위가 된다. CSS 우선순위 !important 되도록 안 쓰는게 좋다. Inline 스타일 div 안에 바로 style 넣은 것 ID로 지정 class…","html":"<h1 id=\"css\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css\" aria-label=\"css permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Cascading Style Sheets</li>\n<li>HTML 문서를 시각적으로 예쁘게 꾸며준다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>Cascading(위에서부터 우선순위)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Author style</li>\n<li>User style</li>\n<li>Browser</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>!important</p>\n<ul>\n<li>cascading을 끊어내고 가장 우선순위가 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"css-우선순위\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-%EC%9A%B0%EC%84%A0%EC%88%9C%EC%9C%84\" aria-label=\"css 우선순위 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS 우선순위</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>!important</p>\n<ul>\n<li>되도록 안 쓰는게 좋다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Inline 스타일</p>\n<ul>\n<li>div 안에 바로 style 넣은 것</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>ID로 지정</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">#special</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> skyblue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>class로 지정</p>\n<ul>\n<li>.클래스 이름 {속성값}</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>태그로 지정</li>\n<li>전체 지정</li>\n</ol>\n<p>💡 특징적이고 구체적인 것일수록 우선순위가 높다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"사용-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"사용 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>사용 방법</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>inline</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>직접 쓰기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\">...</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>internal</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;head></code>에 선언</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>style</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token style\"><span class=\"token language-css\">\n  ...<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>external</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>외부에서 css 파일을 가져와 적용하기 (가장 많이 쓰는 방법)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>link</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">rel</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>stylesheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>text/css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>main.css<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>rel: 현재 파일과 link되는 파일 사이의 관계를 명시</li>\n<li>type: 연결되는 파일 타입 명시</li>\n<li>href: 연결되는 파일 URL 제공</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"css-기본-형태\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%ED%98%95%ED%83%9C\" aria-label=\"css 기본 형태 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS 기본 형태</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Tag 선택자</li>\n<li>Class 선택자</li>\n<li>Id 선택자</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"선택자-구성-요소\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EC%9E%90-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1-%EC%9A%94%EC%86%8C\" aria-label=\"선택자 구성 요소 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>선택자 구성 요소</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1165px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 29.000000000000004%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"selector\"\n        title=\"selector\"\n        src=\"/static/2ff898aac22963b3835baa3116c66d02/96220/selector.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2ff898aac22963b3835baa3116c66d02/5a46d/selector.png 300w,\n/static/2ff898aac22963b3835baa3116c66d02/0a47e/selector.png 600w,\n/static/2ff898aac22963b3835baa3116c66d02/96220/selector.png 1165w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1165px) 100vw, 1165px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>선택자(selector): 어떤 HTML 요소에 스타일을 입힐 것인지를 선택</p>\n<ul>\n<li>e.g. h1</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>속성(attribute): 무엇을</p>\n<ul>\n<li>e.g. color</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>속성값(value): 어떻게 바꿀까?</p>\n<ul>\n<li>e.g. red</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"id-vs-class\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#id-vs-class\" aria-label=\"id vs class permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Id vs Class</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>id</p>\n<ul>\n<li>한 페이지에서 유일</li>\n<li>태그 당 한 개의 id만 가진다.</li>\n<li>문서 구조를 나눌 때 사용한다.\ne.g. <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div id = \"header\"></code></li>\n<li>class로 적용된 스타일을 덮어씌울 때 사용한다.</li>\n<li>남용하면 좋지 않다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>class</p>\n<ul>\n<li>한 페이지에서 반복해서 사용할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>한 태그에 여러개 class를 적용할 수 있다.</li>\n<li>재활용할 수 있는 스타일을 지정할 때 사용한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">.header { color: #ffffff; }</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"선택자-사용-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EC%9E%90-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"선택자 사용 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>선택자 사용 방법</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Universal *</li>\n<li>type Tag</li>\n<li>ID #id</li>\n<li>Class .class</li>\n<li>State :</li>\n<li>\n<p>Attribute []</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* naver로 시작하는 요소들만 초록색 지정 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">a[href^='naver']</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* .com으로 끝나는 요소들만 보라색 지정 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">a[href$='.com']</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> purple<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>선택자는 중첩하여 사용할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">li#special</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> pink<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"css-속성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#css-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"css 속성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS 속성</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>color : 글씨 색상</li>\n<li>\n<p>font-size: 폰트 크기</p>\n<ul>\n<li>em: parent element의 크기가 20px이라면</li>\n<li>1em = 20px</li>\n<li>0.5em = 10px</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>font-family : 글씨체</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">h1 { font-family: Georgia, serif; }</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>width : 너비</li>\n<li>height : 높이</li>\n<li>\n<p>margin : 여백 (바깥) = 요소 바깥 여백</p>\n<ul>\n<li>margin top, right, bottom, left 시계방향 or 위아래/양옆으로 한 번에 지정 가능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>padding : 여백 (안쪽) = 요소 안쪽 여백</p>\n<ul>\n<li>padding top, right, bottom, left 시계방향 or 위아래/양옆으로 한 번에 지정 가능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>background-image : 배경</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.hero</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background-image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string url\">'https://content.codecademy.com/projects/make-a-website/lesson-2/bg.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">background-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> cover<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>border : 테두리 두께</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>width, style, color 한 번에 작성 가능</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2px solid #ffffff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#\" aria-label=\" permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-